QuestData.Title: Someone's Missing Arrow
QuestData.Description: <An arrow of rangari make is sticking out of the side of this talbuk. Perhaps Rangari Laara will be interested in your find.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the Rangari Arrow to Rangari Laara at Telaari Station.
QuestData.RewardText: That's MY arrow! Where'd you get it?
